1
00:00:00,540 --> 00:00:03,410
The Cage of Love

2
00:00:03,410 --> 00:00:06,550
<i>Episode 25</i>

3
00:00:08,630 --> 00:00:11,080
Why must you keep harming us?

4
00:00:11,080 --> 00:00:13,610
Aren't you afraid of retribution?

5
00:00:14,960 --> 00:00:18,460
- Sorry.
- What's the use of apologising?

6
00:00:19,680 --> 00:00:21,990
How is my brother?

7
00:00:21,990 --> 00:00:24,930
The injuries are only superficial wounds.

8
00:00:24,930 --> 00:00:28,490
Those people were set on harming him but not critically.

9
00:00:28,490 --> 00:00:32,220
So to say, even though he has many wounds his life is not in danger.

10
00:00:32,220 --> 00:00:36,310
He is already conscious. You can go in to see him but there shouldn't be too many visitors.

11
00:00:36,310 --> 00:00:39,250
Doctor. I would like to know more about the injuries.

12
00:00:39,250 --> 00:00:41,990
Fine. Come with me to my office.

13
00:00:45,820 --> 00:00:49,010
What are you doing? Do you still have the face to see my brother?

14
00:01:03,640 --> 00:01:05,770
- Fei Fei.
- How is your injury?

15
00:01:05,770 --> 00:01:08,010
I'm fine.

16
00:01:09,970 --> 00:01:12,070
Does it hurt very much?

17
00:01:12,070 --> 00:01:15,530
I'm fine.

18
00:01:15,530 --> 00:01:19,610
How could they beat you into such a state?

19
00:01:19,610 --> 00:01:23,920
Didn't they do this because of the secret formula?

20
00:01:26,420 --> 00:01:28,980
It's because of the secret formula again.

21
00:01:29,800 --> 00:01:33,320
Sorry, Brother. It's all my fault.

22
00:01:33,320 --> 00:01:35,880
If I didn't take away the secret formula,

23
00:01:35,880 --> 00:01:38,450
I wouldn't have caused you to be jailed.

24
00:01:38,450 --> 00:01:41,510
This wouldn't have happened.

25
00:01:41,510 --> 00:01:43,070
Sorry.

26
00:01:43,070 --> 00:01:44,850
Fei Fei.

27
00:01:47,720 --> 00:01:50,820
Don't blame yourself.

28
00:01:50,820 --> 00:01:53,420
This is not your fault.

29
00:01:56,060 --> 00:01:59,490
Listen to me. Everything was

30
00:01:59,490 --> 00:02:01,910
planned by me.

31
00:02:04,730 --> 00:02:06,970
What did you just say?

32
00:02:09,080 --> 00:02:13,450
It started from the first day when they approached me for the silk contest.

33
00:02:13,450 --> 00:02:17,000
I already knew what their motive was.

34
00:02:17,860 --> 00:02:22,970
I made use of you to hand over the secret formula to them.

35
00:02:25,440 --> 00:02:27,870
Sorry.

36
00:02:27,870 --> 00:02:32,570
I used and tricked you.

37
00:02:32,570 --> 00:02:34,940
That secret formula is fake.

38
00:02:50,510 --> 00:02:55,970
Fei Fei. All these years, I know that you have been good to me.

39
00:02:57,210 --> 00:03:00,540
Everything that you have done for my family,

40
00:03:00,540 --> 00:03:02,800
I can see very clearly.

41
00:03:02,800 --> 00:03:04,950
I remember it all.

42
00:03:10,890 --> 00:03:15,460
I'm very thankful that during our most difficult times,

43
00:03:15,460 --> 00:03:19,010
you have always been with us.

44
00:03:26,380 --> 00:03:30,220
You will always be my sister.

45
00:03:30,220 --> 00:03:34,020
I will always be your brother.

46
00:03:35,280 --> 00:03:37,630
We will forever

47
00:03:39,630 --> 00:03:42,160
be a family.

48
00:03:51,620 --> 00:03:53,420
Fei Fei.

49
00:03:55,650 --> 00:03:58,090
Do something for me.

50
00:03:59,100 --> 00:04:01,980
Tell Wu Cai Hong to come in here.

51
00:04:02,860 --> 00:04:05,090
Why do you still want to see her?

52
00:04:06,330 --> 00:04:08,590
Be good.

53
00:04:08,590 --> 00:04:10,510
Go now.

54
00:04:40,150 --> 00:04:43,000
How is Jiang Yu? Is he okay?

55
00:04:48,220 --> 00:04:52,010
Go in. He wants to see you.

56
00:05:02,910 --> 00:05:13,900
