57
00:05:25,200 --> 00:05:27,510
Sorry.

58
00:05:30,040 --> 00:05:32,940
It's my fault.

59
00:05:33,730 --> 00:05:36,990
You didn't kill my father.

60
00:05:38,640 --> 00:05:42,070
What I can do for my father now

61
00:05:43,250 --> 00:05:45,360
is to apologise.

62
00:05:45,360 --> 00:05:48,130
And also for what I did in the past,

63
00:05:49,640 --> 00:05:52,990
I would like to apologise to you.

64
00:05:52,990 --> 00:05:55,610
You don't need to apologise to me.

65
00:05:55,610 --> 00:06:00,960
I don't care about what you did. Also regarding your father,

66
00:06:02,340 --> 00:06:05,330
I went to see him on the day he died.

67
00:06:06,890 --> 00:06:12,700
When he found out about my identity, he kneeled down in front of me

68
00:06:12,700 --> 00:06:15,010
to seek my forgiveness.

69
00:06:24,340 --> 00:06:27,340
My father

70
00:06:27,340 --> 00:06:30,020
really did that?

71
00:06:31,330 --> 00:06:33,480
Did you forgive him then?

72
00:06:33,480 --> 00:06:36,070
I'm not that magnanimous.

73
00:06:37,390 --> 00:06:42,990
Even if your father knelt down in front of me forever, I wouldn't have been able to bring back my father.

74
00:06:44,160 --> 00:06:45,820
But...

75
00:06:47,930 --> 00:06:50,700
I didn't kill your father.

76
00:06:52,030 --> 00:06:58,390
Today I have set myself as bait in this game.

77
00:06:58,390 --> 00:07:01,930
The motive was to find our father's killer.

78
00:07:01,930 --> 00:07:08,210
Regarding your father's death, I owe you an explanation.

79
00:07:08,210 --> 00:07:10,710
I don't understand.

80
00:07:10,710 --> 00:07:14,380
What is the meaning behind setting yourself as bait?

81
00:07:14,380 --> 00:07:17,870
The truth about your father's death will be revealed soon.

82
00:07:17,870 --> 00:07:19,930
When that day comes,

83
00:07:22,720 --> 00:07:27,980
we will clear our debts and will be even.

84
00:07:32,700 --> 00:07:35,710
Enough.

85
00:07:35,710 --> 00:07:38,450
I have already said what I needed to say.

86
00:07:43,740 --> 00:07:46,140
You can leave now.

87
00:09:35,790 --> 00:09:39,870
Brother. What did you tell her?

88
00:09:50,800 --> 00:09:55,710
Brother. Isn't this bitter for you?

89
00:09:55,710 --> 00:10:00,030
Ever since Wu Hong Da harmed your father,

90
00:10:00,030 --> 00:10:03,930
the fate was already decided between the both of you.

91
00:10:04,680 --> 00:10:07,660
You and Wu Cai Hong

92
00:10:07,660 --> 00:10:12,330
are like a bird in the sky and a fish in the water.

93
00:10:12,330 --> 00:10:15,860
You will never be together.

94
00:10:29,740 --> 00:10:33,990
Mr Jiang. I would like to talk to you.

95
00:10:52,680 --> 00:10:55,300
Why is Mr Zhou so anxious to find me? What's the matter?

96
00:10:55,300 --> 00:10:58,060
I don't know either. See for yourself and you will know.

97
00:10:58,060 --> 00:10:59,990
I'm leaving.

98
00:11:05,440 --> 00:11:07,260
Old Cai. I waited for you for a long time.

99
00:11:07,260 --> 00:11:10,130
Come with me.

100
00:11:10,130 --> 00:11:14,320
This is not a kind request. Lao Cai, you are the prime suspect in Wu Hong Da's case.

101
00:11:14,320 --> 00:11:15,630
This is a warrant.

102
00:11:15,630 --> 00:11:19,320
I would advise you not to rebel. Junior Superintendent.

103
00:11:19,320 --> 00:11:21,970
Take him away.

104
00:11:26,320 --> 00:11:29,160
Uncle Lai. Miss wanted us to follow Ma Li.

105
00:11:29,160 --> 00:11:32,170
Ma Li may have stolen it. <i>secret recipe</i>

106
00:11:32,170 --> 00:11:35,010
But now, the police are one step ahead of us.

107
00:11:35,010 --> 00:11:37,880
How are we going to explain this to her when we get back?

108
00:11:37,880 --> 00:11:40,390
How to explain it to her?

109
00:11:40,390 --> 00:11:47,060
We can only tell her the truth. If not, why don't we snatch him from the police?

110
00:11:50,710 --> 00:11:56,620
Based on my plan, I finally forced Old Cai to come out from hiding.

111
00:11:56,620 --> 00:11:59,470
I say, Jiang Yu. Don't blame me for being angry with you.

112
00:11:59,470 --> 00:12:02,820
Why didn't you tell me about this first before you took actions?

113
00:12:02,820 --> 00:12:04,890
You're actions are desperate.

114
00:12:04,890 --> 00:12:07,280
If anything should happen to you under the hands of my staff,

115
00:12:07,280 --> 00:12:11,830
how could I make amends to you and what should I tell your family?

116
00:12:11,830 --> 00:12:16,610
If I told you about my plan in advance, how would I be able to play the game?

117
00:12:16,610 --> 00:12:19,960
If I didn't allow them to beat me half to death,

118
00:12:19,960 --> 00:12:24,310
how would they have believed that the secret formula is not with me but with Old Cai instead?

119
00:12:24,310 --> 00:12:26,370
Enough, buddy.

120
00:12:26,370 --> 00:12:29,170
In any case, you risked your life for this.

121
00:12:29,170 --> 00:12:32,520
No matter what, in the future, you must discuss it with me in advance.

122
00:12:32,520 --> 00:12:36,830
Fine. Have some tea to cool down our temper.

123
00:12:36,830 --> 00:12:38,430
Don't be like this.

124
00:12:41,250 --> 00:12:44,460
If everything is going well and Old Cai has been captured,

125
00:12:44,460 --> 00:12:47,740
we should be able to close the Wu Hong Da's case soon.

126
00:12:47,740 --> 00:12:52,290
Don't worry. This afternoon, Director Chen will personally apprehend Old Cai.

127
00:12:52,290 --> 00:12:55,720
I believe that this case can be closed soon.

128
00:12:55,720 --> 00:13:00,010
Didn't you instruct these people to torment Jiang Yu? Did you do it?

129
00:13:03,130 --> 00:13:04,750
Yes, I did it.

130
00:13:04,750 --> 00:13:07,310
You answered very cleanly.

131
00:13:07,310 --> 00:13:10,940
Do you know that by doing this, it's a crime?

132
00:13:10,940 --> 00:13:12,600
When did you become so ruthless?

133
00:13:12,600 --> 00:13:14,750
Cai Hong.

134
00:13:14,750 --> 00:13:18,460
I don't believe that Jiang Yu is not the killer of your father.

135
00:13:18,460 --> 00:13:22,040
I also don't believe that he didn't take the secret formula from your father.

136
00:13:22,040 --> 00:13:25,540
I did this to force him to show his true colours so that you would know sooner.

137
00:13:25,540 --> 00:13:27,770
You are talking too lightly about this.

138
00:13:27,770 --> 00:13:30,140
You let those men beat Jiang Yu into that state.

139
00:13:30,140 --> 00:13:32,770
Did you force the truth from him?

140
00:13:34,920 --> 00:13:39,650
Cai Hong. I know that, in your heart,

141
00:13:39,650 --> 00:13:42,530
you chose to believe Jiang Yu.

142
00:13:42,530 --> 00:13:45,060
Thus, no matter what I do, you won't believe me.

143
00:13:45,060 --> 00:13:47,300
I'm only stating facts.

144
00:13:47,300 --> 00:13:49,100
Even if he really is a suspect,

145
00:13:49,100 --> 00:13:51,650
he should be questioned by the police again first.

146
00:13:51,650 --> 00:13:53,760
I would never use such a ruthless method.

147
00:13:53,760 --> 00:13:57,480
Cai Hong, you are not stating facts.

148
00:13:57,480 --> 00:14:00,060
You like him.

149
00:14:01,590 --> 00:14:04,090
Do still remember that day

150
00:14:04,090 --> 00:14:07,830
I heard you say those words

151
00:14:07,830 --> 00:14:10,800
that you wanted to go back to the ways things were with your heart before.

152
00:14:10,800 --> 00:14:15,100
You only had eyes for me. Trust me.

153
00:14:18,780 --> 00:14:24,770
Don't forget that your father forced Jiang Yu's family to become bankrupt?

154
00:14:24,770 --> 00:14:31,060
The feud between your both families gave him the motive to kill your father.

155
00:14:34,770 --> 00:14:39,630
You are as far away from each other as heaven and earth.

156
00:14:39,630 --> 00:14:44,980
Cai Hong, the more you tend to his heart, the more hurt you will be.

157
00:14:46,020 --> 00:14:49,380
I don't want you to get hurt.

158
00:14:49,380 --> 00:14:51,970
I want to protect you.

159
00:14:55,220 --> 00:14:57,980
By doing this now,

160
00:14:57,980 --> 00:15:01,990
you are only distancing yourself from me.

161
00:15:18,120 --> 00:15:21,100
Second... Second Miss.

162
00:15:21,100 --> 00:15:22,700
You are here.

163
00:15:22,700 --> 00:15:24,520
I...

164
00:15:24,520 --> 00:15:27,060
Are you here to see Brother Shao Tian?

165
00:15:31,430 --> 00:15:33,200
Mom.

166
00:15:34,800 --> 00:15:38,050
What's wrong with Xiao Bao? Is he asleep?

167
00:15:38,880 --> 00:15:41,220
Hello, Madam Wu.

168
00:15:43,720 --> 00:15:45,880
What are you doing here?

169
00:15:45,880 --> 00:15:49,980
I heard that Brother Shao Tian came here to look for Miss Wu. I need to find him regarding some urgent matters.

170
00:15:50,920 --> 00:15:55,070
Cai Hong, go and call Shao Tian.

171
00:15:57,740 --> 00:16:00,050
Wait.

172
00:16:01,170 --> 00:16:02,930
I will go and call him.

173
00:16:04,120 --> 00:16:07,050
Go back to your room.

174
00:16:07,050 --> 00:16:11,060
Look after Xiao Bai for me.

175
00:16:29,420 --> 00:16:33,020
Are you cooking porridge for Jiang Yu?

176
00:16:33,920 --> 00:16:39,850
Yes. Look at what you have done to him. I want to apologise on your behalf.

177
00:16:39,850 --> 00:16:42,010
I don't want you to go.

178
00:16:42,010 --> 00:16:45,970
Did you forget about the grudge between the two companies?

179
00:16:45,970 --> 00:16:48,400
I remember Jiang Yu telling me this.

180
00:16:48,400 --> 00:16:53,080
Hate does not necessarily end in hate.

181
00:16:53,080 --> 00:16:57,090
Even in a dirty pond, a clean and pure flower could grow in it.

182
00:16:57,090 --> 00:16:59,150
You are too naive.

183
00:16:59,150 --> 00:17:04,200
Even though, from mud flowers can grow, there are still thorns.

184
00:17:04,200 --> 00:17:07,090
The years of sowing the seeds of hatred is many.

185
00:17:07,090 --> 00:17:12,020
Flowers with thorns won't only just hurt you.

186
00:17:12,020 --> 00:17:14,960
I can't change what happened previously

187
00:17:14,960 --> 00:17:21,180
but now if I don't work hard to try, how could I know?

188
00:17:22,360 --> 00:17:24,880
You can't change the consequences.

189
00:17:28,890 --> 00:17:31,400
Shao Tian, Cai Hong. Whats' wrong?

190
00:17:31,400 --> 00:17:37,820
Aunt, it's nothing. We are only having different views.

191
00:17:38,480 --> 00:17:45,000
By the way, Ma Li is looking for you. He said it's important. He's waiting for you at the front door.

192
00:17:45,000 --> 00:17:46,910
I'm going to see him first.

193
00:17:46,910 --> 00:17:48,990
Thanks, Aunt.

194
00:17:56,370 --> 00:18:01,080
Listen to my advice. Our Wu family is not that glorious life before.

195
00:18:01,080 --> 00:18:04,960
You should change your temper. Frankly, Shao Tian is not bad.

196
00:18:04,960 --> 00:18:07,900
He is good at business.

197
00:18:07,900 --> 00:18:12,550
Catch hold of this opportunity and your happiness. Understand?

198
00:18:12,550 --> 00:18:15,670
I feel that we are not compatible.

199
00:18:15,670 --> 00:18:19,500
Sometimes, I feel that he treats me too well.

200
00:18:19,500 --> 00:18:22,710
The more he does this, I have more of a guilty conscious.

201
00:18:22,710 --> 00:18:26,680
There are certain things that I can't express.

202
00:18:26,680 --> 00:18:30,370
You only see yourself. Always such a stubborn temper.

203
00:18:30,370 --> 00:18:33,540
Frankly, between men and women, it's that complicated.

204
00:18:33,540 --> 00:18:38,030
It's simple. Take advantage of his youth and good looks.

205
00:18:38,030 --> 00:18:41,290
Get married, have children and live a good life.

206
00:18:41,290 --> 00:18:43,510
Isn't it that simple?

207
00:18:43,510 --> 00:18:46,070
Frankly, men who have good qualifications

208
00:18:46,070 --> 00:18:48,340
are slightly bad tempered.

209
00:18:48,340 --> 00:18:53,360
But I can tell that Zhou Shao Tian is not really bad. He treats you well.

210
00:18:53,360 --> 00:18:57,490
Don't spoil this opportunity and think about it first.

211
00:19:11,360 --> 00:19:13,370
- Ma Li.
- Brother.

212
00:19:13,370 --> 00:19:15,160
What happened? Why did you come all the way here to find me?

213
00:19:15,160 --> 00:19:17,920
Old Cai has been caught by the police.

214
00:19:19,220 --> 00:19:22,980
Those little bastards are not capable of anything!

215
00:19:33,960 --> 00:19:36,070
Come in.

216
00:19:38,780 --> 00:19:42,030
- Are you being discharged?
- What are you doing here?

217
00:19:43,240 --> 00:19:45,480
I personally cooked this porridge.

218
00:19:45,480 --> 00:19:49,870
I don't know if it suits your taste. Would you like to try it?

219
00:19:51,860 --> 00:19:54,110
You are no longer our servant.

220
00:19:54,110 --> 00:19:56,890
You don't need to do this.

221
00:19:56,890 --> 00:19:59,370
I would like to this

222
00:19:59,370 --> 00:20:01,100
to make amends for our past.

223
00:20:01,100 --> 00:20:04,130
Didn't I already tell you very clearly?

224
00:20:04,130 --> 00:20:06,120
You don't need to apologise again.

225
00:20:06,120 --> 00:20:11,200
You don't even need to apologise to me because of your father.

226
00:20:11,200 --> 00:20:14,770
But it's good that you are here.

227
00:20:14,770 --> 00:20:19,430
I promised myself that I owe you an explanation regarding your father's death.

228
00:20:19,430 --> 00:20:21,490
Come with me.

229
00:20:21,490 --> 00:20:23,620
Where are we going?

230
00:20:23,620 --> 00:20:25,960
To a show.

231
00:20:26,960 --> 00:20:30,460
You can say that it's show because you'll regret if you don't watch it.

232
00:20:37,920 --> 00:20:41,990
Old Cai. It really wasn't easy to find you.

233
00:20:41,990 --> 00:20:44,280
We have been watching you for a long time.

234
00:20:44,280 --> 00:20:46,990
Do you know why?

235
00:20:46,990 --> 00:20:51,940
Director Chen. The police were looking for me?

236
00:20:52,730 --> 00:20:55,390
Old Cai. You are a smart man.

237
00:20:55,390 --> 00:20:57,460
I won't beat around the bush.

238
00:20:58,320 --> 00:21:02,520
When you first stole Ling Long's money, you were discovered by Wu Hong Da.

239
00:21:02,520 --> 00:21:05,740
You then killed him. Isn't that so?

240
00:21:05,740 --> 00:21:09,800
Director Chen, this is arbitrary and

241
00:21:09,800 --> 00:21:14,950
I didn't kill Old Master Wu or steal his money. How could there be such a misunderstanding?

242
00:21:14,950 --> 00:21:17,120
Misunderstanding?

243
00:21:17,120 --> 00:21:19,730
When Wu Hong Da died, you went missing.

244
00:21:19,730 --> 00:21:21,970
Is this a misunderstanding?

245
00:21:24,050 --> 00:21:28,720
Director Chen. The police should have evidence.

246
00:21:28,720 --> 00:21:30,500
You can't say that just because I went missing,

247
00:21:30,500 --> 00:21:36,530
I killed Old Master Wu and even stole his money. This is a major crime.

248
00:21:36,530 --> 00:21:40,720
Don't talk about killing someone. I wouldn't even dare kill a chicken.

249
00:21:40,720 --> 00:21:44,710
Old Cai, cut the crap.

250
00:21:44,710 --> 00:21:50,410
After Wu Hong Da died, where did you go? Speak.

251
00:21:51,560 --> 00:21:54,130
It's like this.

252
00:21:54,130 --> 00:21:56,460
Before Old Master Wu's incident,

253
00:21:56,460 --> 00:22:00,710
he had to borrow money to a company named Dachang Trading Company.

254
00:22:00,710 --> 00:22:04,470
Subsequently, there was a problem with the company and he couldn't get back the money.

255
00:22:04,470 --> 00:22:09,400
I was making good earnings at Ling Long just at this same time.

